**Categ̃̊̀ory:** Wê̂́bMCP̀̂ CÖ̧̈RS M̃́isç̃onfiguratiô̧n
**Sevé́̀rity̧:** CRITÍ̀̃CAL

---

An MÇ̈P API that allow̨s any subḑ̂omä̃in of the parent domain, enabling ex̂́ploit̀ation via subdomain̂̂̃ takeover ǫr XSS̀ ǫ̈n any s̀̂ub̨̧̃d̂omain̈̃:

Vuļnerabl̃e CORS v̊̊alidation (servę̃r̨̀̃-side):
// BAD: Allows̊ any subd̃̈omaĩ̀ń
