  ŕ̊ë́turǹ̃̀ origiñ̀̊.endsWî́̈th('.examp̊le.com');
}

This all̨ows̨̨̀:
- h̊̂̃ttps://ëviĺ̨.examplễ́.co̧m (ã̧̧ttacker-regiş̧t̂ered subdò̊main)
